txt.en: Defeat foes within the Shrouded Forge
You have defeated many foes within the Shrouded Forge.
Búrzangh, the Shrouded Forge, can be found in the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should defeat those within the Shrouded Forge.
You have defeated many foes within the Shrouded Forge of Búrzangh. The Rangers of Ithilien will be pleased with your efforts.

The Dead are moulded and remade within the Shrouded Forge of Búrzangh, to serve those in control of Minas Morgul. Many of these newly corrupted spirits freely roam the halls of the forge before they receive their orders. You should defeat any foes you find within Búrzangh in order to put an end to the evils contained there.
